 null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1018617, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! So and so son of so and so (here take the name of the oppressor) is oppressing me and troubling me making me unhappy and degrading and insulting me. Put him at the mercy of his own soul and remove his support, make him dependent on others and snatch away Your bounties from him, discontinue his sustenance, shorter his life span, deface him and make his enemies overpower him who capture him in his place of safety in the same way as he has done oppression on me, laid a trap for me, made me burn in fire, insulted and degraded me. O Allah! Through You I seek refuge from so and so (here mention his name) because You are the greatest subduer and the one to punish severely.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Khuda wanda! Fula’n bin fula’n mujh par zulm karta hai, aur sitam dhata hai, mujhe takleef di, aur dhoka diya, jalaaya, aur zaleel kiya ya ruswa kiya. Khuda wanda! Usko uske nafs ke hawaale kar de, uske sahaare (support) gira de, usko jald as jald gharaz mand bana de apni ne’mate us se chheen le, uski rozi rok de, uski umr ko kam kar de, uska nishaan mita de, us par uske dushman musallat kar de, uski amaan-gah mein usey pakad le jaise us ne mujh par zulm o sitam kiye hai. Mere liye jaal bichhaaye, aur aag mein tadpaaya, zaleel kiya, ruswa kiya. Khuda wanda! Tere zariye fula’n bin fula’n se panah maangta hu, kyu’n keh Tu bada saaheb’e qaher aur sakht saza dene waala hai.", "Urdu": "خدا وندا! فلاں فرزند فلاں مجھ پر ظلم کرتا ہے اور ستم ڈھاتا ہے، مجھے تکلیف دی اور دکھ دیا، جلایا اور ذلیل کیا، یا رسوا کیا۔ خدا وندا! اس کو اس کے نفص کے حوالے کر دے، اس کے سہارے گرا دے، اس کو جلد از جلد غرض مند بنا دے، اپنی نعمت اس سے چھین لے، اس کی روزی روک دے، اس کی عمر کوتاہ کر دے، اس کا نشان مٹا دے اس پر اس کے دشمن مسلط کر دے، اس کی امان گاہ میں اسے پکڑلے جیسے اس نے مجھ پر ظلم و ستم کیے ہیں۔ میرے لئے جال بچھائے اور آگ میں تڑپایا، ذلیل کیا، رسوا کیا۔ خدا وندا! تیرے ذریعے فلاں بن فؒاں سے پناہ مانگتا ہوں کیونکہ تو بڑا صاحب قہر اور سخت سزا دینے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "SORRY NOT AVAILABLE", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّ فُلَانِ بْنُ فُلَانٍ ظَلَمَنِیْ وَاعْتَدٰی عَلَیَّ وَنَصَبَ لِیْ وَاَمَضَّنِیْ وَاَرْمَضَنِیْ وَاَذَلَّنِیْ وَاَخْلَقَنِیْ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ فَكِلْهُ اِلٰی نَفْسِهٖ وَهُدَّ رُكْنَهٗ وَعَجِّلْ جَائَجَتَهُ وَاَسْلِبْهُ نِعْمَتَكَ عِنْدَهٗ وَاقْطَعْ رِزْقَهٗ وَابْتَرَ عَمْرَهٗ وَامْحُ اَثَرَهٗ وَسَلِّطْ عَلَیْهِ عَدُوَّهٗ وَخُذْهُ فِیْ مَا مَنِهٖ كَمَا ظَلَمَنِیْ وَاعْتَدٰی عَلَیَّ وَنَصَبَ لِیْ وَاَرْمَضَ وَاَذَلَّ وَاَخْلَقَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْتَعِیْذُ بِكَ عَلٰی فُلَانِ بْنِ فُلَانٍ فَاَعِذْنِیْ فَاِنَّكَ اَشَدُّ بَاسًا وَاَشَدُّ تَنْكِیْلًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19":